overview.en: Yearn Finance Dot platform is powerful enough from a scalability, interoperability, developability and governance perspective to help make the vision of Web3 a reality that aims to get more value for an investment.
overview.zh: 从可伸缩性，互操作性，可开发性和治理的角度来看，Yearn Finance Dot平台具有足够强大的功能，可以帮助实现Web3的愿景，旨在为投资带来更多价值。
